Class IDHCPServer

java.lang.Object
  com.sun.xml.ws.commons.virtualbox.VBoxObject
      com.sun.xml.ws.commons.virtualbox.IDHCPServer

public class IDHCPServer
extends VBoxObject

The IDHCPServer interface represents the vbox dhcp server configuration. To enumerate all the dhcp servers on the host, use the IVirtualBox#DHCPServers attribute.
